articles.title: India's Jaishankar hails 'positive trajectory' in China ties - DW
articles.description: Indian Foreign Minister Jaishankar said during a visit to Beijing that India supports China's SCO leadership. It comes after New Delhi indicated it wanted to permanently resolve a Himalayan border dispute.
